---

<section id="mission" class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/442407/pexels-photo-442407.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600')] bg-cover bg-center opacity-10 z-0"></div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our <span class="text-leaf-500">Mission</span></h2>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
          At JägerADS, we're committed to the preservation of bees and their vital role in our ecosystem through technology and education.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-leaf-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-leaf-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-1">Conservation First</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We develop technology that prioritizes bee health and colony preservation above all else.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-leaf-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-leaf-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M2 10.5a1.5 1.5 0 113 0v6a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0v-6zM6 10.333v5.43a2 2 0 001.106 1.79l.05.025A4 4 0 008.943 18h5.416a2 2 0 001.962-1.608l1.2-6A2 2 0 0015.56 8H12V4a2 2 0 00-2-2 1 1 0 00-1 1v.667a4 4 0 01-.8 2.4L6.8 7.933a4 4 0 00-.8 2.4z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-1">Sustainable Beekeeping</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We promote practices that ensure both bee health and sustainable honey production.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-leaf-100 p-2 rounded-full mr-4 mt-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-leaf-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-1">Educational Outreach</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We're committed to educating the public about the importance of bees to our ecosystem.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="#" class="text-leaf-600 hover:text-leaf-700 font-medium inline-flex items-center transition-colors duration-300">
            Learn more about our conservation efforts
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
          <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-leaf-50 rounded-lg border border-leaf-100">
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
              "By protecting our bees, we're not just saving honey – we're preserving the future of our food systems and natural ecosystems."
            </p>
            <p class="text-right mt-2 text-leaf-600 font-medium">– Dr. Emma Chen</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-honey-400 rounded-full opacity-50 z-0 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-16 h-16 bg-leaf-300 rounded-full opacity-40 z-0 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>